      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To prohibit Federal funding for educational agencies and schools whose students do not read certain foundational texts of the United States and are not able to recite those texts or that teach that those texts are products of white supremacy or racism.</title>
      </item>
